---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How Beginner Finance Hub handles your information."
>
  <article>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: June 2026</em></p>

    <h2>What this site is</h2>
    <p>Beginner Finance Hub is a personal finance education website. It does not sell products, require account creation, or collect payment information.</p>

    <h2>What information is collected</h2>
    <p>This site does not directly collect personal information from visitors. When you visit, Netlify (our hosting provider) may log standard server data such as your IP address, browser type, and the pages you request. This is standard for any website and is outside our direct control. See <a href="https://www.netlify.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Netlify's privacy policy</a> for details.</p>

    <p>If you contact us by email, we receive whatever information you include in that message. We use it only to respond to you and do not share it with third parties.</p>

    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>We may add a privacy-respecting analytics tool in the future to understand how content is being used. If we do, this policy will be updated before any tracking is active.</p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>This site does not currently use cookies or tracking pixels beyond what Netlify may set for infrastructure purposes.</p>

    <h2>Third-party links</h2>
    <p>Articles on this site may link to external websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites.</p>

    <h2>Children</h2>
    <p>This site is not directed at children under 13 and does not knowingly collect information from them.</p>

    <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
    <p>If this policy changes in a meaningful way, the "last updated" date above will reflect that. Significant changes will be noted here.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this policy? <a href="/contact">Get in touch.</a></p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
